### EPUB Structure Extractor API
### Requires the REST Client extension (humao.rest-client)

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000
@apiUrl = {{baseUrl}}/api/v1
@epubPath = /workspace/extractor/my_book.epub
@jsonOutput = /workspace/extractor/output/book_with_summaries.json
@marpOutput = /workspace/extractor/output/book_presentation.md

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────
# Health
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────

### Root
GET {{baseUrl}}/

### Health check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health


# ─────────────────────────────────────────────
# EPUB Processing
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────

### 1. Check LLM connectivity (Ollama)
GET {{apiUrl}}/epub/llm/status

### 2. Extract EPUB structure → JSON
POST {{apiUrl}}/epub/extract
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "epub_path": "{{epubPath}}",
  "json_output": "{{jsonOutput}}"
}

### 3. Generate AI summaries (requires Ollama — run step 2 first)
POST {{apiUrl}}/epub/summarize
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "json_path": "{{jsonOutput}}"
}

### 4. Generate Marp presentation (run step 2 first)
POST {{apiUrl}}/epub/marp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "json_path": "{{jsonOutput}}",
  "marp_output": "{{marpOutput}}",
  "title": "My Book Summary",
  "include_summaries": true,
  "include_content": false,
  "max_depth": 3
}

### 5. List sections of an extracted book
GET {{apiUrl}}/epub/sections?book_key={{jsonOutput}}

### 6. Set excluded sections (run step 2 first)
POST {{apiUrl}}/epub/sections/exclude
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "book_key": "{{jsonOutput}}",
  "excluded_ids": ["1", "2.1","3","4","5","6","21","22"],
  "excluded_titles": ["Review Questions"]
}

